# id: RestartStrategy -> void restart(RestartCallback restarter, ScheduledExecutor executor)_
commentText:
Called by the ExecutionGraph to eventually trigger a full recovery._The recovery must be triggered on the given callback object, and may be delayed_with the help of the given scheduled executor.__

The thread that calls this method is not supposed to block/sleep.__@param restarter The hook to restart the ExecutionGraph_@param executor An scheduled executor to delay the restart
